				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Since neither LDA nor EOR affect the C flag, you should end up with 0 or 1 in A, corresponding to whether C was set before you started.<br /><br />ADC <em>always</em> does A←A+C+argument.<br /><br />It doesn't matter whether the +1 in the correction after the EOR comes from #immediate or from C.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

